      <ul class="card-items clearfix center-items">
        <li class="card-item">
          <div class="img">
            <img src="../Img/Home/Team/eric-siu.jpg" alt="Eric Siu" />
          </div>
          <div class="content">
            <h3>Eric Siu</h3>
            <p>Eric is the founder of Single Grain, a digital marketing agency that helps companies such as Uber, SalesForce, TurboTax, KitchenAid, Random House, Sony Pictures, and Nordstrom grow.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="card-item">
          <div class="img">
            <img src="../Img/Home/Team/caio-beleza.jpg" alt="Caio Beleza" />
          </div>
          <div class="content">
            <h3>Caio Beleza</h3>
            <p>Caio is a partner of NPBR International LTDA, an ad agency focused on the Latin America market. He is in charge of operations and making sure companies grow their revenue through digital marketing.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
